or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Install it Yourself: Dishwasher Water Line and Power Cord Kit › or Delivery + Professional Installation It's Working When We Leave We'll deliver, install and make sure your new dishwasher is working. We'll disconnect, haul away and recycle your old dishwasher.** To purchase and schedule this service, select Delivery + Professional Installation during check out or call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289). Required Additional Parts: Dishwasher Water Line and Power Cord Kit › Required Existing Connections 110V power adjacent or near the opening for your new dishwasher Functioning water shutoff valve Compatible water source Potential Additional Charges Required local permit fees Installation of power outlet if your current dishwasher is hard-wired, if required by local code Bringing utilities up to code Replacement of incompatible or non-functioning connections Garbage disposal installation Extensive labor for removal of old dishwasher Preparation for Installation Help your installation go smoothly: Clear the area under your sink Empty your old dishwasher Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the dishwasher Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Refrigerator With Ice and Water Dispenser Delivery Only (Installation May Vary) We'll deliver major appliance purchases totaling $399 or more for free*. If you have an existing water supply line with an accessible, functional, and dedicated water shutoff valve within 6 feet of the refrigerator (or, if greater than 6 feet, an existing copper water supply line), we will install your refrigerator as part of the delivery service, as long as you have purchased a new water line kit (see below) and no modifications are needed to accommodate this kit. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of refrigerator; confirmation of make and model Connection of a new 6-ft. water line between existing shut-off valve and refrigerator or between an existing copper water line and refrigerator, as long as no modifications are needed to accommodate this new water line Optional haul-away and recycling of your old refrigerator** IMPORTANT: With Delivery Only Service, we cannot install a new water supply line or water shutoff valve for your refrigerator. Please call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) to purchase and schedule installation services. Preparation for Delivery: Help your delivery service go smoothly: Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the refrigerator Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Required Additional Parts: Stainless Steel Refrigerator Water Line Kit › or Delivery + Professional Installation It's Working When We Leave We'll deliver, install and make sure your new refrigerator is working. We'll disconnect, haul away and recycle your old refrigerator.** To purchase water supply line or water shutoff valve installation, please call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289). Required Additional Parts: Stainless Steel Refrigerator Water Line Kit › Required Existing Connections Compatible water source within 20 feet of your refrigerator Potential Additional Charges Required local permit fees Installation of water supply lines longer than 20 feet or that require work in crawl spaces Cabinetry modifications Preparation for Installation Help your installation go smoothly: Empty your old refrigerator Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the refrigerator; pay attention to banisters and railings because delivery team cannot lift over waist height Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Refrigerator Without Ice or Water Dispenser Delivery Only (No Installation Needed) It's Working When We Leave We'll deliver major appliance purchases totaling $399 or more for free*. We'll deliver and make sure your new refrigerator is working when we leave. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of refrigerator; confirmation of make and model Level refrigerator and adjust door swing, as needed Optional haul-away and recycling of your old refrigerator** Preparation for Delivery: Help your delivery service go smoothly: Empty your old refrigerator Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the refrigerator; pay attention to banisters and railings because delivery team cannot lift over waist height Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Electric Range Delivery Only (No Installation Needed) It's Working When We Leave We'll deliver major appliance purchases totaling $399 or more for free*. We'll deliver and make sure your new electric range is working when we leave. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of electric range; confirmation of make and model Installation of an anti-tip bracket (requires drilling into floor or wall behind your range) Optional haul-away and recycling of your old electric range** IMPORTANT:You must purchase a new power cord for your new electric range. New ranges do not come with a cord; existing power cords cannot be reused. Preparation for Delivery Help your delivery go smoothly: Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the range Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Required Additional Parts: Range Power Cord › Gas Range Delivery Only (No Installation) We'll Drop It Off and Unbox It Gas appliance installation service may be required for an additional fee. Call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) to determine if it's required. Online gas range appliance orders that require installation also require two separate appointments — one for delivery and one for installation. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of gas range; confirmation of make and model Optional haul-away and recycling of your old range** (if the gas line is already disconnected) IMPORTANT: Some municipalities require licensed professional installation of gas appliances. With Delivery Only Service, we may not be able to connect your range — you must purchase Professional Installation. Call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) to determine if professional installation is required and to schedule an appointment. Preparation for Delivery Help your delivery go smoothly: Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the range Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Install it Yourself: Range Gas Line › or Delivery + Professional Installation It's Working When We Leave If you live in an area that requires a licensed professional to install gas appliances, you must purchase Professional Installation. We'll deliver, install, and make sure your new gas range is working. This includes installation of an anti-tip bracket, which requires drilling into the floor or wall behind your range. Plus, we'll disconnect, haul away and recycle your old gas range.** To find out what is required in your area and to purchase and schedule this service, please call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289). Required Additional Parts: Range Gas Line › Required Existing Connections Functional gas shutoff valve behind range Potential Additional Charges Required local permit fees Replacement of faulty or absent gas shutoff valve Natural gas to liquid propane conversion service, includes conversion kit Preparation for Installation Help your installation go smoothly: Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the range Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Over-the-Range Microwave Shipping Only (No Installation) We'll Ship It To Your Door We offer free shipping on orders $35 and up. All over-the-range microwaves are not delivered but shipped via UPS. or Delivery + Professional Installation It's Working When We Leave We'll ship, install and make sure your new microwave is working. Once you've received your microwave, please call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) to purchase and schedule over-the-range microwave installation. Included with Professional Installation Service: Disconnection and removal of old microwave or range hood Mounting of new microwave Connection to existing utilities and testing Optional haul-away and recycling of your old over-the-range microwave** IMPORTANT: Existing venting direction (inside vs. outside) cannot be changed as part of this service. Required Existing Connections Dedicated 110V electrical outlet Above-range cabinet for mounting Potential Additional Charges Required local permit fees Installation of electrical outlet where hardwired electrical connection is present Preparation for Installation Help your installation go smoothly: Clear cabinet above range Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Cooktop, Wall Oven or Other Built-In Appliance Delivery Only (No Installation) We'll Drop It Off and Unbox It We'll deliver major appliance purchases totaling $399 or more for free*. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of your built-in appliance; confirmation of make and model Optional haul-away and recycling of your old built-in appliance** (if it is disconnected and removed from opening) or Delivery + Professional Installation It's Working When We Leave We'll deliver, install and make sure your new built-in appliance is working. We'll disconnect, haul away and recycle your old appliance.** To purchase built-in appliance installation, please call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289). IMPORTANT: Online built-in appliance orders require two separate appointments — one for delivery and one for installation. Required Existing Connections Each built-in appliance may have different requirements. Please call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) for more details. Required Additional Parts: Each built-in appliance may have different requirements. Please call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) for more details. Potential Additional Charges Each built-in appliance may have different requirements. Please call for more details. Required local permit fees Bringing utilities up to code Replacement of incompatible or non-functioning connections Preparation for Installation Help your installation go smoothly: Clear a path from the street to the kitchen, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the appliance Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Washing Machine Delivery Only (No Installation Needed) It's Working When We Leave We'll deliver major appliance purchases totaling $399 or more for free*. We'll deliver and make sure your new washing machine is working when we leave. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of washing machine; confirmation of make and model Leveling your washer, plugging it in and attaching hoses Front-load washer: placement on matching brand pedestal Optional haul-away and recycling of your old washer** IMPORTANT:You must purchase new fill hoses for your new washer. Some washers do not come with fill hoses; existing fill hoses cannot be reused. Preparation for Delivery Help your delivery go smoothly: Clear a path from the street to the laundry room, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the washer Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Install it Yourself: Stainless Steel Water Hoses › Electric Dryer Delivery Only (No Installation Needed) It's Working When We Leave We'll deliver major appliance purchases totaling $399 or more for free*. We'll deliver and make sure your new electric dryer is working when we leave. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of electric dryer; confirmation of make and model Connection of 220V power cord and vent kit Front-load dryer: Placement on matching brand pedestal and adjustment of door swing Optional haul-away and recycling of your old electric dryer** IMPORTANT:You must purchase a new 220V dryer cord and vent kit for your new dryer. Dryers do not come with a cord or vent kit; existing power cord and exposed venting materials cannot be reused. Preparation for Delivery Help your delivery go smoothly: Clear a path from the street to the laundry room, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the dryer Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Required Additional Parts: Dryer Power Cord › Dryer Vent Kit or Periscope Dryer Vent Kit › Gas Dryer Delivery Only (No Installation) We'll Drop It Off and Unbox It We'll deliver major appliance purchases totaling $399 or more for free*. Gas appliance installation service may be required for an additional fee. Call 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) to determine if it's required. Online gas dryer appliance orders that require installation also require two separate appointments — one for delivery and one for installation. Included with Delivery Only Service: Unboxing and inspection of gas dryer; confirmation of make and model Placement of gas dryer in your laundry room Front-load dryer: Placement on matching brand pedestal and adjustment of door swing Optional haul-away