oom, ensuring it is wide enough to accommodate the dryer Make sure someone 18 or older is present at the appointment time (19 or older in Alabama or Nebraska; 21 or older in Puerto Rico) Questions About Appliance Delivery and Installation? If you have additional questions about what is included with Delivery Only or Delivery Plus Professional Installation Services, or if you need to make changes to your already-scheduled appointment, call 1-888-BEST BUY. If you scheduled your appliance delivery or installation online, you can now change your delivery appointment online. Find your online order and reschedule › Appliance Haul-Away and Recycling We will haul-away a major appliance from your home for a fee when a qualifying replacement product is delivered by Best Buy Home Delivery. However, in order for us to haul away your old appliances, certain requirements must be met. Refer to appliance type above for more details. Appliances are responsibly recycled by our licensed, third-party recycling partners. The recyclers ensure that the various commodities are sent to end markets to be recycled and repurposed into new products. Learn more about recycling › Free Delivery Delivery Only Service Free On Major Appliance Purchases $399 and Up* Delivery starts at $69.99 for major appliance purchases totaling less than $399. Gas Appliances Delivery and Installation of Gas Ranges and Dryers Some municipalities require licensed professional installation of gas appliances, so you may need to upgrade from our Delivery Only Service to our Delivery + Professional Installation service. Call to determine if professional installation is required in your area and to schedule an appointment: 1-888-BEST BUY (1-888-237-8289) *Free delivery offer applies to standard delivery on major appliance purchases $399 or more, and to limited metro delivery area. Delivery outside a major metropolitan area will include extra charges minus a $69.99 discount. Please call for pricing. Major appliances include standard size or larger refrigerators, ranges, cooktops, wall ovens, range hoods, warming drawers, dishwashers, over-the-range microwaves, freezers & ice makers, washing machines, dryers and laundry pedestals. Excludes prior purchases and Best Buy Outlet items. Additional parts, extensive labor and installation charges are extra. If an item cancellation, certificate, or coupon lowers the total delivery purchase price to less than $399, you will be charged for the delivery cost of the remaining items. Delivery starts at $69.99 for major appliance purchases totaling less than $399. Free delivery and free shipping minimum order values are calculated separately. **Additional fees may apply. GET THE LATEST DEALS & MORE Please enter a valid email address. System Error: Please try again. Thank you. Please check your email. BEST BUY APP Learn more › My Best Buy › View Points and Certificates Learn More Exclusive Offers Sign in or Create Account Credit Cards › Make Payment/Check Balance Credit Card Offers Apply Now Orders & Returns › Order Status Shipping, Delivery & Store Pickup Return & Exchange Promise Price Match Guarantee Pay With Points More Orders & Returns Help Support & Services › Customer Service Protection Plans Installation Trade-In Program Product Recalls More Support & Services Corporate Information Forums, Blog & More Careers Partnerships Conditions of Use Privacy Interest-Based Ads California Privacy Rights CA Supply Chain Transparency Act Facebook Twitter Google Plus Pinterest Mobile Site Give Feedback Prices and offers are subject to change. © 2016 Best Buy. All rights reserved. BEST BUY, the BEST BUY logo, the tag design, MY BEST BUY, and BESTBUY.COM are trademarks of Best Buy and its affiliated companies. TRUSTe Certificate
